 /**
  * Main-process Anthropic POST. Uses Node's built-in `fetch`. The
- * response is captured as `{ status, ok, text }` so the renderer
- * can inspect HTTP status and JSON-parse the body itself —
- * matching how the gh client returns raw text and lets the
- * provider service map shapes.
